# 02-Architecture## Mandates

- **Structure**: Use a Monorepo for code-sharing between the core SaaS app and white-label/customer sites.
- **Core Principle**: Enforce strict separation of concerns (frontend/backend).
- **Logic Placement**: Keep all business logic and external API calls (especially Stripe) in Server Components or dedicated API Routes/Server Actions.
